<form action="/api/users" method="post" class="formulario" >
    
    <h1>Registrate</h1>
     <div class="contenedor">
     
        <div class="input-contenedor">
            <i class="fas fa-user icon"></i>
            <input type="text" id="first_name" placeholder="Nombre Completo" name="first_name" required>
        </div>
         
        <div class="input-contenedor">
            <i class="fas fa-user icon"></i>
            <input type="text" id="last_name" placeholder="Apellido" name="last_name" required>
        </div>
         
        <div class="input-contenedor">
            <i class="fas fa-envelope icon"></i>
            <input type="text" id="email" placeholder="Email" name="email" required>
        </div>
         
        <div class="input-contenedor">
            <i class="fas fa-key icon"></i>
            <input type="password" id="password" placeholder="Contraseña" name="password" required>
        </div>
         
        <div class="input-contenedor">
            <i class="fas fa-user icon"></i>
            <input type="text" id="age" placeholder="Edad" name="age" required>
        </div>
         
        <button type="submit" class="button">Registrate</button>
        <p>Al registrarte, aceptas nuestras Condiciones de uso y Política de privacidad.</p>
        <p>¿Ya tienes una cuenta?<a class="link" href="/login">Iniciar Sesion</a></p>
    </div>
</form>